(373, 'anapauo', '\\~anapauw\\~ anapauo', '\\@an-ap-ow''-o\\@', 'from \\\\303\\\\ and \\\\3973\\\\', 'TDNT - 1:350,56', 'v', 'rest 4, refresh 4, take rest 2, give rest 1, take ease 1', 12, ' 1) to cause or permit one to cease from any movement or labour\r\n    in order to recover and collect his strength\r\n 2) to give rest, refresh, to give one''s self rest, take rest\r\n 3) to keep quiet, of calm and patient expectation\r\n'),
