(499, 'antitupos', '\\~antitupov\\~ antitupos', '\\@an-teet''-oo-pon\\@', 'neuter of a compound of \\\\473\\\\ and \\\\5179\\\\', 'TDNT - 8:246,1193', 'adj', 'figure 1, like figure whereinto 1', 2, ' 1) a thing formed after some pattern\r\n 2) a thing resembling another, its counterpart\r\n    2a) something in the Messianic times which answers to the type,\r\n        as baptism corresponds to the deluge (\\\\#1Pe 3:21\\\\)\r\n\r\n Sinonim   : Lihat Definisi \\\\5919\\\\\r\n'),
