(712, 'ariston', '\\~ariston\\~ ariston', '\\@ar''-is-ton\\@', 'apparently neuter of a superlative from the same as \\\\730\\\\', '', 'n n', 'dinner 3', 3, ' 1) the first food taken early in the morning before work, breakfast\r\n 2) later usage: dinner\r\n'),
