(1211, 'de', '\\~dh\\~ de', '\\@day\\@', 'probably akin to \\\\1161\\\\', '', 'particle', 'also 1, now 1, and 1, therefore 1, doubtless 1, not tr 1', 6, ' 1) now, then, verily, in truth, really, surely, certainly\r\n 2) forthwith, at once\r\n'),
