(1213, 'deloo', '\\~dhlow\\~ deloo', '\\@day-lo''-o\\@', 'from \\\\1212\\\\', 'TDNT - 2:61,148', 'v', 'declare 3, signify 3, show 1', 7, ' 1) to make manifest\r\n 2) to make known by relating, to declare\r\n 3) to give one to understand, to indicate, signify\r\n\r\n Sinonim   : Lihat Definisi \\\\5831\\\\\r\n'),
