(1361, 'Diotrephes', '\\~diotrefhv\\~ Diotrephes', '\\@dee-ot-ref-ace''\\@', 'from the alternate of \\\\2203\\\\ and \\\\5142\\\\', '', 'n pr m', 'Diotrephes 1', 1, ' Diotrephes = "nourished by Jove"\r\n\r\n 1) a proud arrogant Christian mentioned in 3 Jo. 9\r\n'),
