(1522, 'eisakouo', '\\~eisakouw\\~ eisakouo', '\\@ice-ak-oo''-o\\@', 'from \\\\1519\\\\ and \\\\191\\\\', 'TDNT - 1:222,34', 'v', 'hear 5', 5, ' 1) to give heed to, comply with admonition, to obey\r\n 2) to listen to, assent to, a request, to be heard, have request\r\n    granted\r\n    2a) of persons offering prayers to God\r\n    2b) of prayers offered up\r\n'),
