(2068, 'esthio', '\\~esyiw\\~ esthio', '\\@es-thee''-o\\@', 'strengthened for a primary \\~edw\\~ edo (to eat) used only in certain tenses, the rest being supplied by \\\\5315\\\\', '', 'v', 'eat 63, live 1, devour 1', 65, ' 1) to eat\r\n 2) to eat (consume) a thing\r\n    2a) to take food, eat a meal\r\n 3) metaph. to devour, consume\r\n'),
