(3444, 'morphe', '\\~morfh\\~ morphe', '\\@mor-fay''\\@', 'perhaps from the base of \\\\3313\\\\ (through the idea of adjustment of parts)', 'TDNT - 4:742,607', 'n f', 'form 3', 3, ' 1) the form by which a person or thing strikes the vision\r\n 2) external appearance\r\n\r\n Sinonim   : Lihat Definisi \\\\5865\\\\\r\n                        dan \\\\5933\\\\\r\n'),
