(5419, 'phrazo', '\\~frazw\\~ phrazo', '\\@frad''-zo\\@', 'probably akin to \\\\5420\\\\ through the idea of defining', '', 'v', 'declare 2', 2, ' 1) to indicate plainly, make known, declare, whether by gesture\r\n    or by writing or speaking, or in some other ways\r\n 2) to explain\r\n'),
